A tiny sea horse that drifts with ocean currents in search of a mate. It swims by circulating water through its hooped fin-like structures.
A large, mutant sea horse. While many sea horses are friendly, Kroaea is dangerous and often attack ships at sea, burning the remnants afterwards.
This massive sea monster crushes ships like toothpicks for sport. Its tentacles can strike so fast that they boil the surrounding water and flay the enemy alive.
